Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.00,0:01:11.67,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}We searched along the rails
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.67,0:01:14.76,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Hoping to find another trail
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.97,0:01:16.47,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Leading to heaven
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.47,0:01:19.05,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}The heavens are waiting for motion
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.05,0:01:21.76,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Fired up for action
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.76,0:01:22.89,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}There's no gain
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.89,0:01:23.64,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Only pain
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.64,0:01:24.47,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Only pain
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.47,0:01:25.18,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Only pain
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.18,0:01:25.93,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Only pain
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.93,0:01:26.77,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}All this pain
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.77,0:01:28.94,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}My pains don't exist to entertain
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.94,0:01:31.36,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Count with me, one two three
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.36,0:01:34.78,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}How many liters can you bleed?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.19,0:01:38.57,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}How many turns you plan to last?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.57,0:01:41.12,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}How many lives you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.58,0:01:43.41,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}I saw a star
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.41,0:01:46.62,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Brightening up the dark
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.87,0:01:55.46,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}So don't you stop my fires from burning our everything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.46,0:02:00.34,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}You and me are nothing but temporary
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.34,0:02:05.64,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Don't you start begging for mercy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.64,0:02:07.14,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}For when I win
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.14,0:02:08.89,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}I won't forgive
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.89,0:02:10.44,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}And I shall win
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.44,0:02:11.98,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}And I shall win
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.98,0:02:18.74,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Yes, I shall win your one-sided game
